predictions.article: China's low-altitude economy boosts smart agriculture
predictions.prediction: The adoption of UAVs in Chinese agriculture will lead to a measurable increase in crop yields and a reduction in pesticide usage by at least 20% within the next quarter.

predictions.article: South Africa's economy returns to growth in the fourth quarter
predictions.prediction: The growth in South Africa's agricultural sector will lead to a 5% increase in agricultural exports in the next quarter.
